{"type":"user.message","data":{"content":"I'm migrating from Xamarin.Forms to .NET MAUI. I used to override OnStart,\nOnSleep, and OnResume in my Application class. What's the equivalent in MAUI?\n","transformedContent":"<current_datetime>2026-04-03T00:50:57.271Z</current_datetime>\n\nI'm migrating from Xamarin.Forms to .NET MAUI. I used to override OnStart,\nOnSleep, and OnResume in my Application class. What's the equivalent in MAUI?","attachments":[],"interactionId":"7cd9cbcd-2262-41cf-bfe9-73ed169cf639"},"id":"d151605a-28fa-480c-a54f-b607f345511e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:50:57.271Z","parentId":"c86d4cd4-3cf1-401d-9f41-5edfec098317"}
